    • Method Detail

      • continueTracking

        boolean continueTracking()
        Continues tracking. This means previously stored locations are not deleted. Returns false if tracking is not possible. (e.G. GPS is turned off)
        Returns:
        true if tracking is possible

      • start

        boolean start()
        Starts tracking with a new track. Returns false if tracking is not possible. (e.G. GPS is turned off)
        Returns:
        true if tracking is possible

      • stop

        void stop()
        Stops tracking.

      • isReady

        boolean isReady()
        Returns true if the tracker is ready. (GPS is turned on)
        Returns:
        true if tracker is ready

      • shutdown

        void shutdown()
        Shutdowns system. Not always necessary.

        Location getLastLocation()
        Returns the most recent location.
        Returns:
        last location

        Returns the current track.
        Returns:
        track
